comment: My family had a really bad experience here. The space doesn't have anything beautiful, just some really boring games. The food is expensive and not worth the price. Staff has very bad service attitude!!! I have never gone to eat anywhere without paper towels like here. When I asked the staff here if they had hand towels, they said no. If you want to wipe your hands, you have to buy cold towels!!!! Will never return to this place.

comment: It's okay. But buying an entrance ticket and having to buy a pool ticket is not very pleasant.

address: 303 Ấp Mỹ Lộc, Mỹ Khánh, Phong Điền, Cần Thơ
comment: The staff's service and the food are very good. But the MC named Hoang Phat was really speechless. Everyone in the world has the right to idolize someone they like. But when this MC found out that our group was coming on November 20, what kind of defamatory words did he say about our idol? After this episode, I lost a lot of sympathy for the MC in particular and the Eco Village in general. I hope that MC's superiors will take action to remind us and apologize to us. Thank you!
